title: Twitter Blue Is An Absolute Dumpster Fire...
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at the Twitter Blue saga, a period where Twitter finally sunsets the legacy verified system and pretty much returns it all within a matter of 48 hours, truly laughable stuff. Thanks for watching!
